<bibRefCitation box="[220,393,1178,1203]" pageId="5" pageNumber="96" refString="Wu, B. L., Sun, R. &amp; Yang, D. (1985) The Nereidae (Polychaetous Annelids) of the Chinese coast. Springer-Verlag, New York, 234 pp." type="book">
